      "span_text": "These hits were counter-screened using an assay developed by the Grembecka lab (University of Michigan) with the Fl-MBM1-menin protein-protein interaction (Fl-MBM1 was used at 15 nM while menin was used at 150 nM).  All of the subsequent hits from the natural product extracts (22 hits) were found to be from lichen extracts isolated in Costa Rica.",
